 </p>\n  </div>\n</template>\n\n<style lang=\"scss\" scoped>\n#azure-warn {\n  background-color: var(--warning);\n  color: var(--warning-text);\n  line-height: 2em;\n  width: 100%;\n\n  > p {\n    text-align: center;\n  }\n}\n</style>\n"]}]}